A 31-year-old man has been arrested for reckless driving and speeding on the R21 near Olifantsfontein. JOHANNESBURG - A 31-year-old man has been arrested for reckless driving and speeding on the R21 near Olifantsfontein. Gauteng Department of Community Safety spokesperson Ofentse Morwane says the man was driving at a 210km/hour, claiming he was rushing to a wedding. Morwane says he is expected to appear in court soon. “He was arrested on the spot and charged with reckless driving. He’s expected to appear in court soon.”